{"tid":190010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"柬埔塞戴腳鐐的大象 枷鎖解開即踩死象主","createTime":"2017-04-07T00:15:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T12:14:56.000Z","uid":122,"like":66,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"49f7d339a39d603c17d5d9e613f95102bf958f06","tid":190010,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T00:15:45.000Z","msg":"<strong>【懷恨在心？】戴腳鐐的大象 枷鎖解開即踩死象主</strong><br />\n<br />\n即時國際 <br />\n<br />\n2017-04-07 07:37:01 HKT<br />\n<br />\n柬埔塞東部一隻被鎖腳鐐的的大象，枷鎖被解開後走脫並將主人踩死。<br />\n<br />\n47歲象主Choeung Team應一群遊客要求，將60歲雄象「Atork」的腳鐐解開，以便他們與象在更自然的環境下合照。<br />\n<br />\n「Atork」枷鎖被解外後，竟蕩進附近森林，Choeung見牠走脫，也追進森林。村民見Choeung遲遲未回，遂四出搜尋，在林中發現Choeung已被「Atork」踩死。<br />\n<br />\nChoeung的姪兒認為叔父被「Atork」用象鼻打，再被踩死。他懷疑「Atork」求偶心切或是對叔父懷恨，所以狂性大發。<br />\n<br />\n警方指「Atork」用來給遊客騎乘以遊覽當地一帶，了解少數民族的生活，懷疑牠處發情期而失常。<br />\n<br />\n「Atork」目前仍未尋回。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》"},{"pid":"7de6f2e6f422c3b15c664b5dc75b8bf531a2807e","tid":190010,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T00:17:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"535a63282d9f8c0e256fab63d2b1fd2666751086","tid":190010,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T00:19:04.000Z","msg":"香港d返工奴隸可以點？<br />\n<br />\n繼續返工啦柒頭"},{"pid":"fc93fb40360223eb80ab55fabbf2cbc0d990a255","tid":190010,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T00:20:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港d返工奴隸可以點？<br />\n<br />\n繼續返工啦柒頭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n連象象都有guts過香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea11231fc977ac610dbce0a13a82133b75062792","tid":190010,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T00:20:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09c9d640d4cb18c9e465e15288127a01f8d5d0aa","tid":190010,"uid":4180